  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 425 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Roll out the flatbread to a thickness of about 1/4 inch.",
    "Brush the olive oil over the flatbread, leaving a small border around the edges.",
    "Sprinkle the shredded smoked mozzarella cheese evenly over the flatbread.",
    "Top the cheese with a layer of fresh spinach leaves.",
    "Sprinkle the minced garlic, salt, black pepper, and red pepper flakes over the spinach.",
    "Bake the flatbread in the preheated oven for 15-20 minutes, or until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Remove the flatbread from the oven and sprinkle with chopped fresh basil.",
    "Slice the flatbread into individual portions and serve immediately."
